init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States is now a third world country, and the rest of the world is a utopia.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States has been in exile for 50 years.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is now a Utopia.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: , while the rest of the world has moved on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the one that caused all the problems.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: America is now the only country in the world that is not part of the Utopia, and it is determined to change that.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and the only way it can do that is by showing the world that it is the only country in the world that is capable of creating a utopia
